<li><span class="indicateur-langue">(<abbr class="abbr" title="Langue&#160;: anglais">en</abbr>)</span> Maggie O'Kane, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/print/0,3858,4561023-103677,00.html">This time I'm scared</a>, <i><a href="/wiki/The_Guardian" title="The Guardian">The Guardian</a></i>, December 5, 2002.</li>
